{"id":9186,"date":"2012-10-29T02:19:30","date_gmt":"2012-10-29T06:19:30","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=9186"},"modified":"2025-03-22T11:02:33","modified_gmt":"2025-03-22T07:02:33","slug":"beware-diseases-baghdah-hasad","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/29\/beware-diseases-baghdah-hasad\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Hatred: Beware spiritual diseases of hate, envy"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Al-Zubayr ibn al-&#8216;Awwam reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Lurking<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>towards you are<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>the diseases of the nations before you. Envy and hatred are the razor. I do not say they shave hair, but rather they shave the religion. <\/strong><strong>By the One in whose hand is my soul, you will not enter Paradise until you have faith, and you will not have faith until you love each other. <\/strong><strong>Shall I tell you what can establish that for you? Spread peace between yourselves.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2510<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <i><strong>Sahih<\/strong> <\/i>(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u064f\u0651\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u062f\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0645\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \